snippet.title: The Political Process Game Trailer
snippet.description:
The game is coming soon to steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1184770/The_Political_Process/

Game Summary: Explore a dynamic world of politics in this turn-based, political simulator. Create a character, run for political office, write legislation, balance budgets, and more as you move up the political hierarchy.

Game Website: https://www.thepoliticalprocess.com/
